Bitzer Mobile Sales Force Contacts Demo Rev 1.1 Dated: 01/08/2011
=====================================================================

Prerequisites:
--------------

* Web server capable of running PHP

Installation steps:
------------------

Deploy MVL:
----------

1. Copy salesforce directory under document root of your web server

2. Open config.php file under includes directory.

3. Enter value for Salesforce API key to $salesforce_api_key line and save the file.

4. Start BMA on iPhone, Android or Blackberry and select Add Library button.

5. Add URL to where you deployed salesforce on your server. e.g.: If you deployed it under
   document root then your URL will be something like this:
   
   http://<your host>:<port>/salesforce/library.php

